## 📅 Execution Roadmap

### Immediate Steps (Next 1-2 Weeks)
1. Complete the 5 critical bug fixes and 2 scope gaps identified in the Minor Project phase.
2. Freeze the codebase and package it for the 6th-semester evaluation.

### Semester 7 Kickoff (Months 1-2)
1. Write the [docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/CipherVault/Code/Projects/Axion%20-%20EV%20Fleet%20Management/Axion-Backend/docker-compose.yml) to include PostgreSQL and TimescaleDB.
2. Build the Spring Boot Kafka Consumer that dumps Canonical Telemetry into TimescaleDB.
3. Migrate all Hardcoded URLs in Java to `application.yml` referencing Docker network outputs.
4. Upgrade the React frontend to use WebSockets instead of polling.

### Semester 7 Midpoint (Months 3-4)
1. Build the Python FastAPI Scikit-learn microservice.
2. Implement the OTA Campaign tracking logic in Postgres via JPA/Hibernate.
3. Build the OTA Campaign UI and the RCA UI components in React.
4. Integrate Spring Security (JWT) and Grafana.
